headline: Atopic Dermatitis Market Forecast Report 2025-2034 | FDA Approval of Tralokinumab-Ldrm Stimulates Treatment Advances
summary: The atopic dermatitis market, valued at USD 9.33 billion in 2024, is projected to grow at a CAGR of 15.10%, reaching USD 38.07 billion by 2034. Key drivers include increasing prevalence, FDA approvals like LEO Pharma's tralokinumab-ldrm, and novel treatments. Major players include AbbVie, Pfizer, and Regeneron.
